title: Find Your Voice
description:
Join Sadie Robertson as she interviews Miles Fidell, Lead Pastor of Auburn Community Church in Auburn, AL. Miles Fidell currently serves in his thriving, multi-generational church reaching thousands of college students and families with the Gospel. Listen as they discuss college ministry, finding your own voice, and the hidden blessing of discomfort and uncertainty.
